        <div class="prose-dark">
          <h2>Schema Plugins for WordPress GEO</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>Schema plugin choice on WordPress is a GEO decision as much as an SEO decision.</strong> The three leading
            options — Yoast SEO Premium, Rank Math Pro, and dedicated schema plugins — produce meaningfully different structured
            data outputs, and the differences matter significantly for AI engine parsing.
          </p>
        </div>

